name: #08 - Discover
description:
(Unmute Sound for Optimal Experience)

Fragment 08 - Discover
(From the BINARY EMOTIONS series)

"One doesn't discover new lands without consenting to lose sight, for a very long time, of the shore. What better way to discover the unknown than to follow your instincts."

Discover: It's dedicated to the nature of discovery and why one is destined to find his world. For one to discover their strengths and hone them, they can be who they want to be. After all, at the center of being, the answers lie waiting to be uncovered. 
--
"BINARY EMOTIONS" is a series based on 12 Single Edition Fragments in which the artist aims to translate his inner nuances within a specific moment into visuals that evoke certain emotions. An emotional journey digitized into a binary piece cataloged onto the blockchain.
